PROGRAM: 

LXI H, 4200H
MVI C, 04H
NEXT: MOV A, M
OUT C0H
LXI D, 1010H
LOOP: DCX D
MOV A, E
ORA D
JNZ LOOP
INX H
DCR C
JNZ NEXT
JMP START
HLT

OUTPUT: 

SWS        CW             ANTI-CW
S1      1  1  0  0       0  0  1  1
S2      0  1  1  0       0  1  1  0
S3      0  0  1  1       1  1  0  0
S4      1  0  0  1       1  0  0  1 

SWS 		- Switching Sequence
S1 		  - Sequence - 1
CW 		  - Clock Wise
ANTI CW - ANTI - Clock Wise
